<D>__{that's a shame. would have been useful.}
<C>__{mark}
<D>__{go ahead, detective.}
<C>__{detective harrison}
<D>__{thank you. brandi, can you remember anything specifically? what color was his hair? was he tall or short?}
<C>__{brandi}
<D>__{he was tall and skinny and he had brown hair and it was real greasy.}
<A>__{detective harrison begins writing in his note pad as brandi speaks. ronnie notices this and picks up some paper and begins to write as well.}
<C>__{detective harrison}
<D>__{was his hair long or short?}
