<D>__{just a brown trench coat.}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{this is what i got so far.}
<A>__{ronnie holds up his paper. ronnie has drawn a crude sketch of the pervert that brandi described, but it's basically a long haired stick figure with a penis.}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{what's yours look like?}
